    Adventure</size>\r\n\r\n<color=#C87840>\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500</color>\r\n\r\n<size=22><color=#
    F0D060>DEVELOPED BY</color></size>\r\n<size=20>Omar Nada</size>\r\n\r\n<color=#C87840>\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500</color>\r\n\r\n\r\n<size=22><color=#
    F0D060>GAME DESIGN & PROGRAMMING</color></size>\r\n<size=20>Omar Nada\r\n\r\n<color=#C87840>\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500</color>\r\n\r\n<size=22><color=#
    F0D060>TOOLS & ENGINE</color></size>\r\n<size=20>\r\nGame Engine \u2014 Unity
    6\r\nVersion Control \u2014 GitHub\r\nSprite Editor \u2014 LibreSprite\r\nAI
    Art \u2014 ChatGPT / DALL-E\r\n\r\n<color=#C87840>\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500</color>\r\n\r\n<size=22><color=#
    F0D060>SOUND EFFECTS</color></size>\r\n<size=16><color=#8B7355>\r\n\u2022\tLarge
    sword swing by Squirrel_404 -- https://freesound.org/s/737748/ -- License: Attribution
    4.0\r\n\u2022\tPlayerHurt2 by mrickey13 -- https://freesound.org/s/515624/ --
    License: Creative Commons 0\r\n\u2022\tEnemy Death (Gaseous) #1 by SilverIllusionist
    -- https://freesound.org/s/833358/ -- License: Attribution 4.0\r\n\u2022\tSick
    Fly Enemy Dead Sound by AUDACITIER -- https://freesound.org/s/632240/ -- License:
    Attribution 4.0\r\n\u2022\tZombie Attack by soykevin -- https://freesound.org/s/213509/
    -- License: Creative Commons 0\r\n\u2022\tmonster bite by LucasDuff -- https://freesound.org/s/467701/
    -- License: Creative Commons 0\r\n\u2022\tVelcro Pull 01 by Rudmer_Rotteveel
    -- https://freesound.org/s/536231/ -- License: Creative Commons 0\r\n\u2022\tMonster
    Roar_8.mp3 by mitchanary -- https://freesound.org/s/505131/ -- License: Attribution
    4.0\r\n\u2022\tplayer_death_ui_show.wav by nfsmaster821 -- https://freesound.org/s/697867/
    -- License: Creative Commons 0\r\n\u2022\tZombie Growl by 137SOUNDS -- https://freesound.org/s/241269/
    -- License: Attribution 3.0\r\n\u2022\tGame Pickup by IENBA -- https://freesound.org/s/698768/
    -- License: Creative Commons 0\r\n\u2022\t8-Bit Coin Or Power Up FX For Retro
    Video Games by Cloud-10 -- https://freesound.org/s/647977/ -- License: Creative
    Commons 0\r\n\u2022\tBreaking A Wall Down (With A Hammer) by scampsie -- https://freesound.org/s/417091/
    -- License: Attribution 3.0\r\n\u2022\tWrong by Raclure -- https://freesound.org/s/483598/
    -- License: Creative Commons 0\r\n\u2022\tMosquito Buzz (Vocal Talent) by Idalize
    -- https://freesound.org/s/410145/ -- License: Attribution NonCommercial 4.0\r\n\u2022\tWind-up
    sound by Breviceps -- https://freesound.org/s/445966/ -- License: Creative Commons
    0\r\n\u2022\tWhoosh / Dash by Kastenfrosch -- https://freesound.org/s/521999/
    -- License: Creative Commons 0\r\n\u2022\tSpider Eat 2 by Frostnox -- https://freesound.org/s/837906/
    -- License: Attribution 4.0\r\n\u2022\tMonster Roar_8.mp3 by mitchanary -- https://freesound.org/s/505131/
    -- License: Attribution 4.0\r\n\u2022\tSword Stab  Body Hit by -GeorgeDiamond-
    -- https://freesound.org/s/718259/ -- License: Attribution 4.0\r\n\u2022\tKnife
    throw.mp3 by Gingie -- https://freesound.org/s/181679/ -- License: Creative Commons
    0\r\n\u2022\tgrunt1.wav by Michel88 -- https://freesound.org/s/76963/ -- License:
    Sampling+\r\n\u2022\tpaind.wav by Michel88 -- https://freesound.org/s/76966/
    -- License: Sampling+\r\n\u2022\tKnife throw.mp3 by Gingie -- https://freesound.org/s/181679/
    -- License: Creative Commons 0\r\n\u2022\tSword - Unsheathe by Vrymaa -- https://freesound.org/s/770035/
    -- License: Creative Commons 0\r\n\u2022\tMonster Short Roar.wav by ecfike --
    https://freesound.org/s/132874/ -- License: Creative Commons 0\r\n\u2022\tMonster
    Growl #2 by SamsCollegeAccount -- https://freesound.org/s/722985/ -- License:
    Creative Commons 0\r\n\r\n</color></size>\r\n\r\n<size=22><color=#D4A017>MUSIC</color></size>\r\n<size=16><color=#8B7355>\r\n\u2022\tthe
    hidden temple by tullio -- https://freesound.org/s/712013/ -- License: Creative
    Commons 0\r\n</color></size>\r\n\r\n<color=#C87840>\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500</color>\r\n<size=22>\r\nMade
    with \u2764 and too much coffee\r\n\r\n\xA9 [2026] [Omar Nada]\r\nAll Rights
    Reserved\r\n</size>\r\n"
